# NOTE: stb_image.h / stb_image_write.h used to be excluded here (the
# user downloaded them locally rather than this repo vendoring them).
# As of devdocs/DEV_LOG.md section 25 (session 3), the user provided the
# real files directly and they are now genuinely vendored in
# third_party/ -- so they must NOT be gitignored anymore, or a fresh
# clone would be missing them despite README.md's Quick start no longer
# even mentioning a download step for the common case. Found this stale
# rule still present during session 4's cleanup pass (see section 30) --
# fixed here rather than left as a latent "looks fine until someone does
# a fresh clone" trap.

# Generated test/demo outputs (images, volumes the user creates while
# trying the tool -- not part of the source tree)
*.rawvol
output/*.png
output/*.rawvol
data/*.png
data/*.jpg
data/*.rawvol
!data/README.md
!output/README.md

# OS/editor cruft
